## Welcoming our new co-founder, Eva Decker

Co-founder Eva Decker and I have been building with worker-owned software consulting co-op [Computost](https://www.computost.com/) to reenvision Namesake and its future. We want to build accessible, ethical technology that empowers and connects people. 

