## Growing an online community

While we continue to rebuild, the old site will continue to run so that you’ll still have access to Namesake’s resources. And in the meantime, we’ve launched a Discord where you can find community and support no matter where you are in the process (Want to practice using some new names? We got you). We hope this can be a space where we can all exchange tips and information as well as celebrate each other.

We’re excited to launch our new app later this year. If you want to get involved, join our Discord and let’s chat.
